{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-044","title":"婉言拒绝","sectionId":"chapter-02","sectionTitle":"日常交际你最强","pageStart":238,"pageEnd":242,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":22,"duplicateEntryCount":9,"pages":[{"number":238,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"44 婉言拒绝"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"rejection [rɪˈdʒekʃn]","headword":"rejection"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.拒绝"},{"type":"note","text":"◎proposal rejection拒绝建议，回绝倡议"},{"type":"entry","text":"refusal [rɪˈfjuːzl]","headword":"refusal"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.拒绝（对公正处理﹑权利等的拒绝，拒不给予）"},{"type":"entry","text":"exclude [ɪkˈskluːd]","headword":"exclude"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.拒绝接纳；不让…入内"},{"type":"note","text":"◎exclude from使…不得进入"}]},{"number":239,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"turn down 拒绝","headword":"turn down"},{"type":"entry","text":"mood [muːd]","headword":"mood"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.语气；情绪，心绪"},{"type":"note","text":"◎not in the mood没心情"},{"type":"entry","text":"mild [maɪld]","headword":"mild"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.温和的"},{"type":"entry","text":"heartfelt [ˈhɑːtfelt]","headword":"heartfelt"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.衷心的"},{"type":"entry","text":"excuse [ɪkˈskjuːs]","headword":"excuse"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.借口"},{"type":"note","text":"◎excuse for …的借口"},{"type":"entry","text":"reason [ˈriːzn]","headword":"reason"}]},{"number":240,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"n.原因"},{"type":"note","text":"◎reason for …的原因"},{"type":"entry","text":"standpoint [ˈstændpɔɪnt]","headword":"standpoint"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.立场"},{"type":"entry","text":"time [taɪm]","headword":"time"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.时间"},{"type":"note","text":"◎out of time没时间"},{"type":"entry","text":"inconvenience [ˌɪnkənˈviːniəns]","headword":"inconvenience"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.不方便"},{"type":"entry","text":"change the subject 转移话题","headword":"change the subject"},{"type":"entry","text":"listen to 倾听","headword":"listen to"},{"type":"entry","text":"advice [ədˈvaɪs]","headword":"advice"}]},{"number":241,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"n.建议"},{"type":"entry","text":"concern [kənˈsɜːn]","headword":"concern"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.关心"},{"type":"entry","text":"with regret 遗憾地","headword":"with regret"},{"type":"entry","text":"doubt [daʊt]","headword":"doubt"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.怀疑"},{"type":"text","text":"I doubt it. 不一定。/我表示怀疑。"},{"type":"entry","text":"afraid [əˈfreɪd]","headword":"afraid"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.恐怕的"},{"type":"entry","text":"other plan 其他计划","headword":"other plan"},{"type":"entry","text":"fully scheduled 日程已满","headword":"fully scheduled"},{"type":"entry","text":"take a raincheck 改天","headword":"take a raincheck"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：My boss is refusing my report because it's 10 minutes late. （我老"},{"type":"text","text":"板拒绝听我的报告，因为晚了10分钟。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Maybe I could help you in some way.（也许我能帮上忙。）"}]},{"number":242,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：He told me that you refused to discuss the matter.（他告诉我你"},{"type":"text","text":"拒绝和他讨论这件事。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：What nonsense! I never talked to him in my life! （胡说！我这辈"},{"type":"text","text":"子连话都没跟他说过！）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 3"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Hey, Marsha, how about we going for dinner and a movie tonight?"},{"type":"text","text":"（嗨，玛莎，我们今晚一起吃饭看电影怎么样？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I'm afraid I can't. I have other plans.（恐怕我不能去。我有其他"},{"type":"text","text":"安排。）"}]}]}